Payment System


Who handles credit card processing? 
Third party apps such as sas stripe, square.

How many transaactions a day? 
One million

What are the flows in a payment system? 
  pay in flow - Money from customers (via payment system) to sellers
  pay out flow -money from payment system to sellers

Non functional requirements
Resilience and fault tolerance.

What is PSP?
PSP is payment service provider.

